H0.text: What type of animal is a dik-dik. Gazelle

H1.text: What type of animal is a dik-dik. Rodent

H2.text: What type of animal is a dik-dik. Cheetah

H3.text: What type of animal is a dik-dik. Antelope

A4.text: The dik-diks are four species of small antelope in the genus Madoqua

A5.text: Dik-diks are herbivores. Their diet mainly consists of foliage, shoots, fruit and berries, but little or no grass.
